high_descs: Turn around and go towards the bed.
Pick up the pot from the bed.
Turn around and head towards the two doors in the corner of the room, then take the one on the left, turn left and immediately right into the kitchen area to the fridge.
Place the pot into the fridge, let it cool, then retrieve it.
Return to the room you got the pot from and go to the sidetable next to the bed.
Place the pot on the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Cool a pot in a fridge and place it on a side table.

high_descs: Turn around to walk to the bed.
Pick up the pot from the bed.
Turn around and walk into the passage on the left and walk to the kitchen to reach the fridge.
Cool the pot in the fridge and take it out.
Turn around to walk down the passage and turn right to reach the bedroom sidetable.
Put the pot on the sidetable behind the white board.
anns.task_desc: Put the cooled pot on the side table.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the bed.
Pick up the black pot off of the bed.
Facing forward go through the door on the left take a left and then a right into the kitchen and go to the fridge.
Put the pot in the refrigerator and then take the pot back out.
Turn left and then another left on the hallway and then a right into the sidetable.
Put the pot behind the white shade on the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled Pot on the SideTable.
